+- `fcntl07`, `fcntl07_64`, `fcntl11`, `fcntl11_64`, `fcntl12`, `fcntl12_64`.
+- `epoll_ctl02`, `epoll_ctl04`, `epoll_wait02`, `epoll_wait05`, `epoll_pwait03`.
+
